{"tid":275123,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"條仔好暴力","createTime":"2017-06-07T19:51:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T12:13:53.000Z","uid":26761,"like":12,"dislike":74,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8bf54bfdf4f10543c92ade375db44ad59f1059b8","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:51:03.000Z","msg":"是咁的 今日同條仔嘈交 之後佢無啦啦好激動 用手掐住我條頸 推咗我埋石壆 撞到嗰下feel到好痛 如果驗傷嘅話絕對告得入佢傷人 但之後佢猛咁say sorry 話佢知錯 又話以後都唔會咁 但之前有幾次比佢暴力對待完佢都係咁講 但佢次次都話其實佢好愛我嘅 所以各位巴絲比下意見 我仲應唔應該信佢 定係分手<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇野嘅 打者愛也<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分手啦 打女人正賤男"},{"pid":"bf44284b405621415985072084f1c00d0559c5ba","tid":275123,"uid":77546,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T19:52:20.000Z","msg":"暴力=無條件分手"},{"pid":"b9154cca9fa16c1e9ff08a403ff4e13743978508","tid":275123,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T20:40:37.000Z","msg":"叫佢床上面都咁暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dd778cd5782a5fb94699933dcb7307853faf210","tid":275123,"uid":121841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:46:49.000Z","msg":"我係咪識你男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"117f6ebd9f9fec4e2cd119126bcd347a1b273578","tid":275123,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:49:40.000Z","msg":"分手啦<br />\n結左婚打到你仆街<br />\n生左仔女又係打佢地"},{"pid":"d6cb11fdda939d96baa63061208c62877d7b3e46","tid":275123,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:51:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82f1ea029648653dfba7dca48909708486780ae4","tid":275123,"uid":117868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T21:57:39.000Z","msg":"你都問得"},{