8ab7555448edd36fda9d38383a1040","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:58:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪你講野太臭閪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我有時啲性格係難頂啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可能佢忍得我好辛苦"},{"pid":"30a67dd82f0c7061f5e9555df05d28bd10922ce8","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T07:59:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>叫佢含返你當無數</blockquote><br />\n我係藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6977efc0f8ef2ec309d6433932bf3f733240a3d9","tid":275123,"uid":112198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:01:02.000Z","msg":"真係愛你會對你用咁嘅程度嘅暴力咩？<br />\n醒下喇傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c722ed493ec985c2220fac2efcd1fe000e510c","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:04:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常有理性嘅人都唔會郁手郁腳啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要用暴力方式去發泄只係顯示到佢情緒管理有問題<br />\n分手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />拖得愈長愈唔捨得 以後就知味道</blockquote><br />\n但佢真係知錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 喺我面前喊哂口好冇尊嚴咁 所以我決定比多最後一次機會佢 希望佢以後識得好好控制自己啲情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋佢呢排大壓力 我都想體諒佢多啲關心佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然今次佢過份咗 但平時佢對我好好 所以我真心覺得可以比多次機會佢"},{"pid":"255774ffaed77f213b14b179e5613d68e0d9503e","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分啦，咩都唔好諗，之前打過你，你都仲同佢一齊<br />\n其實你係縱容緊佢，佢會愈黎愈覺得打女人唔係咩大事<br />\n打完講句對唔住就搞掂<br />\n你而家咁縱容佢，其實係害緊你自己同害埋佢<br />\n呢樣野真係唔可以容忍，其實第一次打你果陣就應該即分<br />\n咁佢先會明咁樣做既後果係幾咁嚴重<br />\n而家佢已經進入慢慢習慣打女人既心態<br />\n再唔分，你搵定個好既跌打師傅同佢過世啦<br />\n唔好再放佢出黎害人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129dfd028b7d86f1225e250b26a3b4e08d0ed664","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:06:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主係m？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男朋係s嘅話我就係m<br />\n佢係m嘅話 我就係s"},{"pid":"f315c0c19262e60e2bdd10c8378f0e323c585359","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係愛你會對你用咁嘅程度嘅暴力咩？<br />\n醒下喇傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我明啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我都只係比多最後一次機會佢啫<br />\n佢都知今次係最後一次機會 會好好珍惜"},{"pid":"5cc24a200c4f99c2e7bf383db56fdf43525dcccc","tid":275123,"uid":26761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主係m？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男朋係s嘅話我就係m<br />\n佢係m嘅話 我就係s</blockquote><br />\n男朋<span style=\"color: red;\">友</span>"},{"pid":"a09d850df713ac9534fd1c3119c2e39cf15a3f87","tid":275123,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:10:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>叫佢床上面都咁暴力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n情趣來的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b324faa64d25c761052dc3c6da8bffb3ac24cb6","tid":275123,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:12:25.000Z","msg":"咩事嘈先？<br />\n如果帽事<br />\n打到你傷殘都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他嘢就唔應該打咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ecac6dcdb06626e177c8fee01d55caec76f731","tid":275123,"uid":57158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:28:54.000Z","msg":"叉頸喎 想你死先會叉頸 唔該你唔好放佢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d323be31d28934252edc08baff84e0153915323","tid":275123,"uid":108134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:29:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c84083446fee8de7e05d8788fb26cd22b03b1d34","tid":275123,"uid":56421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"容忍只會令對方得寸進尺 調轉頭諗愛你就唔會打你啦"},{"pid":"8c732ec2c5ac91627d68a222e0c909ab25dc8b38","tid":275123,"uid":35598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:38:00.000Z","msg":"你撞親個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ba162126b27b9dd46a2841d721375e49b037b3","tid":275123,"uid":68143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T08:43:12.000Z","msg":"打得一次就有第二次"}]}